'''
The objective of this program is to be able to convert miles to other units
Input the set number of miles
Convert the miles to various units like yards, feet, or inches
Print out these conversions
@author Jaqx

miles = int(input("# of miles"))

feet = miles * 5280

print(str(miles) + "miles" + "converts to" + str(feet) + "feet")



yards = miles * 1760

print(str(miles) + "miles" + "converts to" + str(yards) + "yards")



inches = miles * 63,360
print(str(miles) + "miles" + "converts to" + str(inches) + "inches")